  Mash bananas. Lightly beat egg, milk &amp; yoghurt together. Add bananas to dry
  ingredients. Pour melted butter &amp; egg mixture into the well &amp; mix with a
  fork until JUST combined. Spoon into prepared pans &amp; bake at 430Ã¸F for
